results.name: Continued fraction for L(2, chi3), where L(s, chi3) is the Dirichlet L-function for the non-principal character modulo 3.
formula: chi3(k) = Kronecker(-3, k); chi3(k) is 0, 1, -1 when k reduced modulo 3 is 0, 1, 2, respectively; chi3 is A102283.
program: (PARI) contfrac(zetahurwitz(2,1/3)/9 - zetahurwitz(2,2/3)/9) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jan 31 2018
